# Package Manager

- This repository uses `bun.lock`, so install dependencies with `bun add` or `bun install`.
- Use Bun instead of npm for package operations:
  - `bun add <package>` instead of `npm install <package>`
  - `bun install` instead of `npm install`
  - `bun run <script>` instead of `npm run <script>`
  - `bunx <command>` instead of `npx <command>` unless project docs explicitly require `npx`
- Do not add an npm lockfile.
